<h1><a href="http://www.admail.net/info/email-marketing/" style="text-decoration: none;" title="Email Marketing Information">Email Marketing Services &amp; Contact Management</a></h1>
<div class="main-copy">
Admail.net is a <a href="/info/services/" title="Admail.net Email Marketing Services">set of tools</a>
that allow you to create and deploy professional
<a href="/info/email-marketing/" title="Email Marketing Information">email marketing campaigns</a>.
Built around <a href="/info/about-us/" title="Admail.net's Story">16 years
of email marketing experience</a>, Admail is a robust and powerful
way to manage your list and send highly deliverable email campaigns
without extensive technical expertise. Services include
<a class="product" href="/info/listbuilder/" title="More about List Builder">List&nbsp;Builder</a>&#8482;,
<a class="product" href="/info/emailbuilder/" title="More about Email Builder">Email&nbsp;Builder</a>&#8482; and
<a class="product" href="/info/accutrak/" title="More about AccuTrak">AccuTrak</a>&#8482;;
each designed to make your list management, email building, and statistic
tracking experiences as simple as possible.
<a class="product" href="/join.php" title="Free Trial of Admail.net">Try Admail today</a>
to see how email marketing can benefit your business or organization.
</div>
